snippet.title: Parkitect 'Extreme' Trailer
snippet.description:
Build your own ADRENALINE MEGALOPOLIS in Parkitect. Coming to Steam Early Access on May 5th!
Our Steam store page is live now:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/453090
Also, check out our devlog for weekly updates: http://devlog.themeparkitect.com

Site: http://themeparkitect.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ParkitectGame
